uot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Zerif Lite Theme" data-image-description="&lt;p&gt;https://wordpress.org/themes/zerif-lite/&lt;/p&gt;\n" data-medium-file="http://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/onepage-screenshots_zeriflite-233x300.jpg" data-large-file="http://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/onepage-screenshots_zeriflite-796x1024.jpg" /></a>\n\n<hr />\n<h4>Links to Download These Themes</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/twentysixteen/" target="_blank">Twenty Sixteen Theme</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://www.memberlitetheme.com/" target="_blank">Memberlite Theme</a></li>\n<li><a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/activello/" target="_blank">Activello Theme</a></li>\n<li><a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/sydney/" target="_blank">Sydney Theme</a></li>\n<li><a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/zerif-lite/" target="_blank">Zerif Lite Theme</a></li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<h2>Need to capture more information or integrate with a third party?</h2>\n<p>Here are a few commonly used add ons that would fit with the landing page membership site model:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href="http://www.paidmembershipspro.com/add-ons/free-add-ons/pmpro-register-helper-add-checkout-and-profile-fields/" target="_blank">Register Helper Add On</a> to collect additional profile fields about your members.</li>\n<li><a href="http://www.paidmembershipspro.com/add-ons/free-add-ons/email-templates-admin-editor/" target="_blank">Email Templates Admin Editor Add On</a> to customize the member communications sent from your site.</li>\n<li><a href="http://www.paidmembershipspro.com/add-ons/plus-add-ons/member-homepages/" target="_blank">Member Homepages Add On</a> allows you to set a DIFFERENT landing page/homepage for your members after logging in. This would allow you to show the download to your eBook, details about the event or an overview of your newsletter program.</li>\n<li><a href="http://www.paidmembershipspro.com/add-ons/plus-add-ons/shipping-address-membership-checkout/" target="_blank">Shipping Address Add On</a> to collect a shipping address for physical goods.</li>\n<li>Email Marketing Integration for <a href="http://www.paidmembershipspro.com/add-ons/free-add-ons/pmpro-mailchimp-integration/" target="_blank">MailChimp</a>, <a href="http://www.paidmembershipspro.com/add-ons/free-add-ons/pmpro-aweber-integration/" target="_blank">Aweber</a>, <a href="http://www.paidmembershipspro.com/add-ons/free-add-ons/convertkit-integration/" target="_blank">ConvertKit</a> or <a href="http://www.paidmembershipspro.com/add-ons/free-add-ons/pmpro-constant-contact/" target="_blank">Constant Contact</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<p>I hope this tutorial gets you excited to set up a &#8220;pop up&#8221; membership site to sell a single membership item. Post a comment below if you need more direction for a unique membership model using this &#8220;landing page&#8221; concept. </p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:78:"http://www.paidmembershipspro.com/set-one-page-wordpress-membership-site/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:45:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:76:"Redirect to a Unique 